      "writtenOn": "2019-10-21T23:37:24Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "The reasons are\n- there are some error checking, like invalid index when decoding.\n- a little bit easy to read.\n\nNeither of them are strong reasons, did you suggest to calculate the value directly?",
