        "id": 1133706
      },
      "writtenOn": "2019-10-23T10:16:32Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I would replace with something like\n\n  static inline uint8_t EncodeByte(uint8_t byte) {\n    return (byte \u003e\u003d 94u) ? 0xff : (byte + \u0027!\u0027);\n  }\n\n  static inline uint8_t DecodeByte(uint8_t byte) {\n    return std::min(\n      static_cast\u003cuint8_t\u003e(byte - \u0027!\u0027),\n      static_cast\u003cuint8_t\u003e(94));\n  }\n\nand delete all the table allocation and initialization, and replace lookups with function calls.",
      "parentUuid": "64b40e44_1c417c1c",
