      "writtenOn": "2019-10-21T13:23:53Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Probably a good idea to assert that this can\u0027t be called multiple times, and Write can\u0027t be called after Flush (given that those are documented as the contract in OutputStreamInterface). Maybe initialized_.set_invalid() once flushed?",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 69,
        "startChar": 25,
        "endLine": 69,
        "endChar": 30
      },
      "revId": "1534f84559f5d225614a04af80f14b30291e152f",
