      "message": "I don\u0027t think this is right. Yes, it\u0027s possible to consume one byte and continue at 123, but bit_count_ isn\u0027t incremented there (and would have to be incremented by a fractional value). The only point that bit_count_ is modified is 128-134, and a postcondition of that block of code is that bit_count_ \u003c 8.",
